OL,7,FMartin Hole took over the running of
OL,8,Fthe business from his father-in-law
OL,9,Fwhen he retired at 90 years old. For
OL,10,Fthe last three and a half years,
OL,11,FMartin has been joined by youngest
OL,12,Fdaughter, Romney, who is 25.
OL,14,FBut while Romney was once excited
OL,15,Fabout taking over from her father, now
OL,16,Fshe's fearful about what the future
OL,17,Fholds. Labour's planned inheritance
OL,18,Ftax changes for farmers means she
OL,19,Fcould have an incredible tax bill to
OL,20,Fpay.
