OL,3,CFarmers' protest: "I've never seen
OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion"
OL,7,F"This is about the continuity of the
OL,8,Ffamily businesses, it isn't just about
OL,9,Fjust farming. I've never known a
OL,10,Fmoment in farming crisis when farmers
OL,11,Fhave come to gather so rapidly and so
OL,12,Finstantly and with such emotion as
OL,13,Fthis issue. "
OL,15,FThe government says that up to #3
OL,16,Fmillion can be passed on by two people
OL,17,Ffree of inheritance tax. Anything
OL,18,Fbeyond that will be taxed at 20%,
OL,19,Frather than the usual 40% .
