OL,7,FBut The NFU says it puts the future of
OL,8,Fmany farm businesses under threat.
OL,10,FRomney adds:
OL,12,F"I envisaged a future that my children
OL,13,Fwould grow up here and it would be a
OL,14,Fplace that my family can always come
OL,15,Fhome to and knowing that there are
OL,16,Fgoing to be elements that we are going
OL,17,Fto have to sacrifice, might jeopardise
OL,18,Fthat future and that's a really sad
OL,19,Fposition to be in. "
