OL,7,FThe National Farmers' Union said
OL,8,Fhundreds of Britain's farmers and
OL,9,Fgrowers will take part in a mass lobby
OL,10,Fof their MPs on November 19 to
OL,11,Fhighlight the devastating impact of
OL,12,Fthe recent Budget on their farms, with
OL,13,Fchanges to Agricultural Property
OL,14,FRelief (APR) and Business Property
OL,15,FRelief (BPR).
