OL,3,CFarmers' protest: "I've never seen
OL,4,Cfarmers come together with such
OL,5,Cemotion"
OL,7,F"With public services crumbling, a
OL,8,F#22bn fiscal hole inherited from the
OL,9,Fprevious government and 40% of
OL,10,FAgricultural Property Relief going to
OL,11,Fthe 7% wealthiest claimants, we made a
OL,12,Fdifficult decision to ensure the
OL,13,Frelief is fiscally sustainable.
OL,15,F"Around 500 claims each year will be
OL,16,Fimpacted and farm-owning couples can
OL,17,Fpass on up to #3m without paying any
OL,18,Finheritance tax - this is a fair and
OL,19,Fbalanced approach."
